INSERT INTO streak_user_data (user_id, streak_id, amount, best, latest_time_string)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
        ON CONFLICT (user_id, streak_id) DO UPDATE
        SET amount = EXCLUDED.amount,
            best = EXCLUDED.best,
            latest_time_string = EXCLUDED.latest_time_string
